Package: calltracer
Title: Trace Transitive Function Dependencies in R Code
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("CCBR", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "ccbr@example.org")
  )
Description: Build direct and transitive function dependency graphs from an
    R entry script and a target package source tree. Exports machine-readable
    and human-readable artifacts (CSV, JSON, SVG) for impact analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/CCBR/calltracer
BugReports: https://github.com/CCBR/calltracer/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    grDevices,
    igraph,
    jsonlite,
    readr,
    utils
Suggests:
    covr,
    knitr,
    lintr,
    rmarkdown,
    roxygen2,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    treesitter
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
